  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">From Exploitation in Mines to a Hope Filled Future</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Every day, young children are being exploited to work in the artisanal mines in DR Congo. The hours are long and they are often threatened with violence, all for 8p a day. Operating in Katanga province, close to these mines, Kimbilio is able to offer support to some of these young children; transforming their lives from exploitation to a hope-filled future.  Kimbilio offers holistic support to children who have lost contact with their families and are trying their best just to survive.</narrative>
  </description>
